title: autoRefresh bursts loadCredentials without stagger
updated_at: "2026-07-15T05:22:57Z"
---
## Problem
`autoRefresh` calls `loadCredentials` for every due profile in a tight loop with no stagger. Combined with the shared credReader race this almost guarantees mis-attributed credential reads once 2+ profiles share a refresh window. Manual Refresh is staggered (~2s) but timer refresh is not.

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:747-758

## Suggested fix
Route due-profile refreshes through the same stagger queue as `staggerRefreshAll`, and never start a second credential cat for a profile that is already loading.

